  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Business Processes in Treasury and Risk Management</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"abstract\" content=\"Treasury and Risk Management covers a variety of business processes. The three main processes Foreign Exchange Risk Management, Debt and Investment Management, and Trade Finance each consist of a number of subprocesses.\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Treasury and Risk Management covers a variety of business processes. The three main processes Foreign Exchange Risk Management, Debt and Investment Management, and Trade Finance each consist of a number of subprocesses.\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loio7aed0b1a31aa471ea93f983bf2594f26\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Business Processes in Treasury and Risk Management</h1><div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Treasury and Risk Management covers a variety of business processes. The three main processes <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Foreign Exchange Risk\nManagement</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Debt and Investment Management</span>, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Trade Finance</span> each consist of a\nnumber of subprocesses.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> <div class=\"relinfo\"><div class=\"relinfotitle \">Related Information</div><div><a class=\"link\" href=\"6d0faf56473a6a15e10000000a441470.html\" title=\"End-to-end process that provides comprehensive features and functions, such as exposure and hedge management, to secure against FX risks. Besides management of financial transactions concluded, accurate registration, and a comprehensive view of all business activities aligned with (inter)national accounting principles such as IFRS and US GAAP is also included. The process also covers the integration scenarios with SAP Market Rates Management and SAP Trading Platform Integration applications.\">Foreign Exchange Risk Management</a></div><div><a class=\"link\" href=\"d02a1260556f4f34884996b77b8237df.html\" title=\"Manage your financial investments and borrowings, like fixed or variable interest rate deposits, loans, commercial papers, or investment certificates. Straight-through processing of financial transactions from front office, middle office, back office, and accounting.\">Debt and Investment Management</a></div><div><a class=\"link\" href=\"e07cc955c3be037ce10000000a44147b.html\" title=\"Provides you with specific financial transactions from banks and financial institutions to facilitate local and international trading. Regardless of whether you are the exporter or importer, you can map your processes for processing bank guarantees, letters of credit, and standby letters of credit.\">Trade Finance</a></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}